{"tid":2421702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"預算案宣傳竟打正旗號「阿茂整餅」 市民：張貼紙望落似一碌切咗嘅鳩多啲","createTime":"2021-02-24T16:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T03:04:08.000Z","uid":63183,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"16a2af3e5db5f5e88d87f1a19cc170bb312dbb34","tid":2421702,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=9ccb77f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5451&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Fm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=37d3bce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5451</a><br />\n陳茂波為咗推銷早財政預算案，喺上年12月諮詢嘅時候，就已經用「阿茂整餅」嘅典故拍咗套宣傳片。當時已經有人指出佢唔應該用「阿茂整餅」整餅嘅典故，因為呢句歇後語係「冇嗰樣整嗰樣」，非常負面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAdAkZokiew&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeAdAkZokiew%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Fm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=0c16d77c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAdAkZokiew&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n港語學主席陳樂行就話，身為「阿茂」用負面嘅情況典故包裝自己，情況相當罕有。雖然佢祖籍潮州，但住喺香港幾十年，冇理由唔知「阿茂整餅」係鬧人。「但就弊在佢真係喺預算案『冇嗰樣整嗰樣』，令人唔覺得佢喺度自嘲。」<br />\n<br />\n除咗預算案本身做多咗之外，啲周邊宣傳品亦都受人非議。佢亦都派發貼紙，不過就冇人敢貼喺身上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-3.png?w=560&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D-3.png%3Fw%3D560%26ssl%3D1&h=25f75751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有收到貼紙嘅市民坦言：「點睇都似喺一碌切咗嘅鳩。」"},{"pid":"b135f8b4f73978b3ad2a8b43040e6e9917835798","tid":2421702,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c412eaea223e363cd6a210ff59584787132b59","tid":2421702,"uid":353587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"又「阿茂整餅」、又「一碌切咗嘅鳩」 其實係咪專登玩鳩劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c62e91276be4ce1e39828db98e0d7c0b18bd25","tid":2421702,"uid":230104,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"想塑造（抄襲）品客曾俊華既卡通形象，又唔知自己個撚樣似龜頭柒下柒下"},{"pid":"7163aaf07450ab552e73d3753370c118bd65f2ee","tid":2421702,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9c412eaea223e363cd6a210ff59584787132b59","tid":2421702,"uid":353587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"又「阿茂整餅」、又「一碌切咗嘅鳩」 其實係咪專登玩鳩劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"係玩我哋班蟻民多啲掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cc2367982c1f910a5751205e3863a38cda8812","tid":2421702,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c62e91276be4ce1e39828db98e0d7c0b18bd25","tid":2421702,"uid":230104,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"想塑造（抄襲）品客曾俊華既卡通形象，又唔知自己個撚樣似龜頭柒下柒下"},"cit